001package org.nasdanika.graph.processor;
002
003import org.nasdanika.graph.Connection;
004
005/**
006 * Mix-in interface for processor factories with no-operation endpoints.
007 * @author Pavel
008 *
009 * @param <P> Processor type.
010 * @param <H> Handler type.
011 */
012public interface NopEndpointProcessorFactory<P,H> extends ProcessorFactory<P,H,H> {
013
014        /**
015         * Returns argument handler.
016         */
017        @Override
018        default H createEndpoint(Connection connection, H handler, HandlerType type) {
019                return handler;
020        }
021        
022}
